<p begin="00:02:25.179" end="00:02:27.881" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">BUT IT IS NOW ABUNDANTLY<br/>CLEAR THAT ANY OPPORTUNITY</span></p>
<p begin="00:02:27.915" end="00:02:29.616" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">FOR OUTRAGE OR MORAL PEARL<br/>CLUTCHING THAT WE</span></p>
