<p begin="00:02:55.642" end="00:02:58.111" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">THE SPY ORGANIZATION WAS<br/>UP-- OH, YOU KNOW WHO COULD</span></p>
<p begin="00:02:58.111" end="00:03:06.453" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">HELP US, THE NS-- OH [BLEEP]<br/>IT'S TIME FOR A GOOD OLD US</span></p>
<p begin="00:03:06.486" end="00:03:10.557" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">OF A PLAUSIBLE DENIABILITY<br/>SCRAMBLE.</span></p>
<p begin="00:03:10.591" end="00:03:14.061" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">BROUGHT TO YOU BY, I DON'T<br/>RECALL IF I HAD BEEN</span></p>
<p begin="00:03:14.061" end="00:03:16.063" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">SPECIFICALLY BRIEFED ON<br/>WHETHER OR NOT THIS IS</span></p>
